'''Hangar Bay HF-201''' was the [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] on [[Home One/Legends|''Home One'']] in which the [[Tydirium/Legends|''Tydirium'']] was located prior to it leaving for [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Judder Page/Legends|Judder Page]] met with the group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who had helped free [[Deep Ear]] from [[Pinnacle Keep]] in this hangar before they left for Endor.

